title: Episode 324: What's the Safe-word!? (Feat. Mistress Marley & Beta Bitch)

description:
Dominatrix, Mistress Marley joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and brings her sub, Beta Bitch, along for the ride. Mistress Marley teaches us about life as a dom, how she got into it, all the different types of ways to make money, her family's perspective on her line of work, while Beta Bitch opens up about his high-profile life outside of being a sub, how he got into this, etc. Mistress Marley even demonstrates some flogging and feet worshiping with Beta Bitch!
